\layout Subsection

System Description
\layout Standard

Any visitor to the site will be able to request access by ringing a door
 bell.
 If the user is at their PC, they will be able to run the software to use
 the camera.
 The software will display one still image picture that will be regularly
 updated (approximately one frame every four seconds), this picture will
 be saved as a file.
 The user will be able to communicate with the visitor from the PC.
 If the user is satisfied that this person should have access to the site,
 then they will be able to send a signal to open the door.
\layout Standard

When there is no reply from the user the visitor will be able to gain access
 to the site if they know the correct pin number.
